{"type": "article", "id": 17594, "title": "锯齿纹路立柜", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-16T07:10:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606150236vMTJtcbY10LOhmSD.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tTruly Truly 是荷兰的一个设计工作室，他们喜欢做有创造力的东西。这组立柜将木片削成了不规则的形状，部分重叠，创造出一个锯齿形的轮廓。设计师想探讨自然和非自然的关系，在雪松木衔接处中混入了黑色的大理石，成为一个有层次感的波纹立面。细看时，木材的纹路和大理石的颗粒感都非常清晰，很独特。<a href=\"http://www.studiotrulytruly.com/fuse-cabinet.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144702bLkuq2TgmFhC3ayv.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1490\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.37962963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144711Ivip3k56B4QtC8RV.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"796\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.32666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144711hH5GRN9UIE7rAf1s.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144712jE9vJSXgfnmh4caA.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"900\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}